snippet.title: JoBlo Originals
snippet.description:
JOBLO VIDEOS features all of the original video content series created by those movie-loving fanboys over at JoBlo.com including: WTF HAPPENED TO THIS MOVIE!?, THE BEST MOVIE YOU NEVER SAW, AWFULLY GOOD MOVIES, GONE BUT NOT FORGOTTEN, THE MOVIE THAT ALMOST WAS, WTF HAPPENED TO THIS CELEBRITY?!, JAMES BOND REVISITED, REEL ACTION, FANTASIZING ABOUT FANTASY FILMS, COLLECTOR'S CORNER (schedules below) and more!

WTF Happened to this Movie? (bi-weekly)
The Best Movie You Never Saw (bi-weekly)
WTF Happened to this Celebrity? (bi-weekly)
James Bond Revisited (monthly)
WTF *really* Happened to this Movie (bi-weekly)
Gone but not Forgotten (monthly)
Awfully Good Movies (monthly)
The Movie that Almost Was (monthly)
Reel Action (monthly)
Fantasizing about Fantasy Films (monthly)
Collector's Corner (monthly)
Movie (video) reviews
Tributes

JOBLO was founded by movie fans, operated by movie fans....for movie fans!!
